codex
The compile failure is straightforward: `src/FlawVerifier.sol` defines `interface Vm`, and the test file defines the same name again after importing it. I’m locating the exact test target and then I’ll patch the verifier with the smallest safe rename first, followed by a forge run to catch any runtime issues.
